description: We are introduced to MARSHAL LAW, a sanctioned vigilante who hunts superheroes that have gone rogue. He is superhero himself, an ex-army supersoldier who is disillusioned about so called "superheroes". He operates in the city of San Futuro, San Francisco after "The Big One". He gets in to trail of a serial killer that murders strippers dressed as worlds most famous female superhero, CELESTE.
name: Stars and Strippers

This is a series that details the history of the marvel universe. This issue includes information on:

1) The time line of the marvel universe from its birth to the age of Marvels.

2) Origin of the Fantastic Four.

3) Origin of Canada's Alpha Flight Program

4) Origin of Ant-man

5) The Arrival of the Skrulls.
